---
title: Chili Lime Steak with Charred Corn Salad and Garlic Cumin Rice
description: Kid-friendly and adult-approved: it’s not an easy feat, but this recipe nails it. There’s plenty of variety and flavor for more sophisticated palates, like in the cumin-spiced rice, corn tomato salad, and robust steak topped with chili lime butter. But it’s still well-balanced and stays away from extremes, playing it just safe enough, even for picky eaters.
